1
00:00:48,080 --> 00:00:52,970
[The Ferry Man: 10th Anniversary]

2
00:00:53,480 --> 00:00:55,930
[Episode 7]

3
00:01:06,760 --> 00:01:08,020
Zha, vanquish demons!

4
00:01:19,870 --> 00:01:21,400
What a realistic illusion.

5
00:01:34,509 --> 00:01:35,039
No.

6
00:01:36,039 --> 00:01:37,840
That wasn't your voice just now.

7
00:01:59,350 --> 00:02:00,020
Did you

8
00:02:00,840 --> 00:02:02,020
save us just now?

9
00:02:03,800 --> 00:02:04,930
You two lack skills.

10
00:02:05,230 --> 00:02:06,310
Why did you rush in here

11
00:02:06,310 --> 00:02:07,170
so recklessly?

12
00:02:08,840 --> 00:02:10,240
Who are you saying lacks skill?

13
00:02:10,240 --> 00:02:12,500
I just picked the wrong spiritual paper.

14
00:02:13,150 --> 00:02:15,330
You two are no match for the demons here.

15
00:02:15,330 --> 00:02:16,590
Hurry up and follow me.

16
00:02:24,040 --> 00:02:24,810
Rickshaw.

17
00:02:26,480 --> 00:02:27,640
Excuse me.

18
00:02:30,430 --> 00:02:31,030
Come look.

19
00:02:31,030 --> 00:02:32,079
Our nation is in crisis,

20
00:02:32,079 --> 00:02:33,079
we must take action.

21
00:02:33,079 --> 00:02:33,560
That's right.

22
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:33,970
Today,

23
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,030
we must join the protest.

24
00:02:35,030 --> 00:02:35,590
That's right.

25
00:02:35,590 --> 00:02:36,960
We need to gather our friends.

26
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:38,120
Brothers, together!

27
00:02:38,120 --> 00:02:39,650
Did we travel through time?

28
00:02:39,710 --> 00:02:40,710
It's an illusion.

29
00:02:42,750 --> 00:02:43,880
Is this an illusion?

30
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:46,400
Come take a look.

31
00:02:46,590 --> 00:02:47,680
Of course it is.

32
00:02:48,360 --> 00:02:49,020
Therefore,

33
00:02:49,030 --> 00:02:49,750
don't talk to them

34
00:02:49,750 --> 00:02:50,880
or make eye contact.

35
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:52,430
If they bewitch you,

36
00:02:52,430 --> 00:02:53,630
you'll be in trouble.

37
00:02:54,710 --> 00:02:56,170
Such a lifelike illusion.

38
00:02:56,230 --> 00:02:57,190
This demon is really powerful,

39
00:02:57,190 --> 00:02:57,870
creating such a huge illusion

40
00:02:57,870 --> 00:02:59,000
out of thin air.

41
00:03:01,710 --> 00:03:02,570
Can we eat this?

42
00:03:03,440 --> 00:03:04,480
Of course you can.

43
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:06,380
It's just an illusion,

44
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:07,120
not poison.

45
00:03:08,870 --> 00:03:09,870
In this illusion,

46
00:03:10,190 --> 00:03:11,360
you can also get full.

47
00:03:11,360 --> 00:03:12,470
But once you leave,

48
00:03:12,680 --> 00:03:14,140
you'll feel hungry again.

49
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:21,090
May I ask who you are?

50
00:03:21,430 --> 00:03:22,430
My surname is Bai.

51
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:24,000
Call me Bai Xiaonian.

52
00:03:25,079 --> 00:03:26,630
Don't ask anything more than that.

53
00:03:26,630 --> 00:03:27,240
We are not

54
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:28,640
on the same path, anyway.

55
00:03:28,910 --> 00:03:30,570
I'm here waiting for someone.

56
00:03:33,030 --> 00:03:34,230
Waiting for a friend?

57
00:03:35,750 --> 00:03:36,950
Do you guys know about

58
00:03:37,310 --> 00:03:38,770
the big demon in this town?

59
00:03:41,820 --> 00:03:43,079
I have a friend who was
young and arrogant.

60
00:03:43,079 --> 00:03:44,150
He came to eliminate the demon,

61
00:03:44,150 --> 00:03:45,280
but was caught by it.

62
00:03:46,470 --> 00:03:47,329
I have been looking for him

63
00:03:47,329 --> 00:03:48,660
in this town for 3 years.

64
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:49,910
Three years?

65
00:03:50,630 --> 00:03:51,470
Wouldn't he have been
digested by the demon

66
00:03:51,470 --> 00:03:53,530
and excreted as fertilizer long ago?

67
00:03:53,630 --> 00:03:55,230
It has nothing to do with you.

68
00:03:57,310 --> 00:03:58,590
Speaking of which,

69
00:03:58,910 --> 00:04:00,710
what kind of demon is it exactly?

70
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:01,810
I'm not sure.

71
00:04:02,190 --> 00:04:02,920
I don't know.

72
00:04:03,430 --> 00:04:05,240
Since you are also looking for the demon,

73
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:06,440
the two of us can help.

74
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:10,360
How can you two help?

75
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:13,030
You're here to catch the demon
for money, right?

76
00:04:13,030 --> 00:04:14,680
I've seen many people like you.

77
00:04:14,680 --> 00:04:15,960
You're just causing trouble.

78
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:17,620
You won't be making any money.

79
00:04:18,600 --> 00:04:19,660
If you want to live,

80
00:04:20,070 --> 00:04:21,000
stay close to me.

81
00:04:21,310 --> 00:04:23,170
I'll get you out of here right now.

82
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:27,080
Okay.

83
00:04:27,430 --> 00:04:28,890
I'll leave the money here.

84
00:04:32,560 --> 00:04:33,070
Look.

85
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:41,880
Isn't that Ms. Huang?

86
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:43,100
What Ms. Huang?

87
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:44,930
The person who hired us.

88
00:04:46,360 --> 00:04:47,220
That's not her.

89
00:04:47,310 --> 00:04:48,770
All of this is an illusion.

90
00:04:52,390 --> 00:04:53,520
Let's go take a look.

91
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:08,220
Where did he go?

92
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:09,280
Dongqing.

93
00:05:10,190 --> 00:05:10,800
Dongqing!

94
00:05:11,820 --> 00:05:12,420
Dongqing!

95
00:05:12,510 --> 00:05:13,240
Stop shouting.

96
00:05:13,240 --> 00:05:13,840
Come here.

97
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:15,810
Where did you run off to?

98
00:05:58,600 --> 00:05:59,600
She disappeared.

99
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:02,400
Let's go check out that well.

100
00:06:18,070 --> 00:06:19,530
This well is very strange.

101
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:22,100
There is a special energy on the rope.

102
00:06:22,310 --> 00:06:22,720
Look.

103
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:25,000
But the rope snapped,

104
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:26,770
so the energy has weakened.

105
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:32,560
This rope doesn't look like it snapped.

106
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:40,070
Rather, it was untied by that woman

107
00:06:40,070 --> 00:06:41,330
who looks exactly like

108
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:42,560
Huang Shang.

109
00:06:46,870 --> 00:06:47,730
There is a demon

110
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:49,159
imprisoned in this well.

111
00:06:49,159 --> 00:06:50,120
That woman who looks

112
00:06:50,120 --> 00:06:51,520
exactly like Huang Shang

113
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:53,530
is Huang Shang's ancestor.

114
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:56,310
She was the town witch of her generation.

115
00:06:56,310 --> 00:06:56,830
Generally speaking,

116
00:06:56,830 --> 00:06:58,290
witches protect the town.

117
00:06:58,800 --> 00:06:59,310
You mean...

118
00:06:59,310 --> 00:07:00,240
I mean,

119
00:07:00,750 --> 00:07:02,280
why did she untie the rope

120
00:07:02,310 --> 00:07:03,570
and release the demon?

121
00:07:04,900 --> 00:07:06,300
Stay away from that well!

122
00:07:06,310 --> 00:07:07,120
Bai Xiaonian?

123
00:07:07,390 --> 00:07:08,600
Why did you run off on your own?

124
00:07:08,600 --> 00:07:10,200
There is a demon in this well.

125
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:11,830
I will take you two

126
00:07:11,830 --> 00:07:13,230
out of here immediately.

127
00:07:18,450 --> 00:07:19,960
There's no time. Hurry!

128
00:07:20,660 --> 00:07:22,190
-Zhao Hengzhi, run!
-Stop!

129
00:07:28,310 --> 00:07:29,110
Bai Xiaonian.

130
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:30,720
I think that demon

131
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:32,430
is you.

132
00:07:32,950 --> 00:07:34,159
How could he be a demon?

133
00:07:34,159 --> 00:07:35,290
He saved us just now.

134
00:07:36,870 --> 00:07:38,070
What are you talking about?

135
00:07:38,070 --> 00:07:39,430
He did that to gain our trust

136
00:07:39,430 --> 00:07:41,360
and trick us into leaving the town.

137
00:07:44,070 --> 00:07:44,870
Bai Xiaonian.

138
00:07:46,510 --> 00:07:48,430
You say this is a demon's lair.

139
00:07:49,630 --> 00:07:50,310
I guess

140
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:52,790
it's yours.

141
00:07:54,270 --> 00:07:54,600
Zhao-

142
00:07:55,950 --> 00:07:57,010
What are you doing?

143
00:07:57,070 --> 00:07:58,360
I'll say it one more time.

144
00:07:58,360 --> 00:07:59,090
Let go of him!

145
00:08:01,600 --> 00:08:02,800
Don't push your luck.

146
00:08:03,070 --> 00:08:04,360
I gave you a way out,

147
00:08:04,920 --> 00:08:06,720
but you insist on seeking death.

148
00:08:07,510 --> 00:08:09,310
You've forced me to play the BGM.

149
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:13,510
The Eighth Spiritual Paper

150
00:08:13,510 --> 00:08:15,560
is the Demon Subduing Formation
of the Zhao family.

151
00:08:15,560 --> 00:08:16,800
When the formation is activated,

152
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:18,800
the spiritual paper will produce
the Samadhi Fire.

153
00:08:18,800 --> 00:08:21,130
Since you're a demon, it'll vanquish you.

154
00:08:36,549 --> 00:08:37,520
Samadhi Fire.

155
00:08:37,630 --> 00:08:38,559
Demon Subduing!

156
00:09:15,340 --> 00:09:16,140
Zhao Hengzhi!

157
00:09:23,870 --> 00:09:24,840
Dongqing!

158
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:31,000
He's missing?

159
00:09:31,150 --> 00:09:31,750
Ms. Huang.

160
00:09:31,790 --> 00:09:33,050
Let's call the police.

161
00:09:33,720 --> 00:09:35,780
How can we tell the police about this?

162
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:37,870
And if the word gets out,

163
00:09:38,250 --> 00:09:39,240
who would dare to come to town

164
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:40,840
and buy houses in the future?

165
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:44,720
You...

166
00:09:45,390 --> 00:09:46,200
You're so fierce.

167
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:47,080
Are you

168
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:48,320
obsessed with money?

169
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:50,910
Here.

170
00:09:56,120 --> 00:09:56,720
What for?

171
00:09:57,030 --> 00:09:58,160
Isn't this my money?

172
00:09:58,270 --> 00:09:58,550
Yes.

173
00:09:59,360 --> 00:10:00,560
Now it's yours again.

174
00:10:01,140 --> 00:10:02,190
Hurry up and come with me

175
00:10:02,190 --> 00:10:03,120
to save my buddy.

176
00:10:03,360 --> 00:10:04,320
This is your reward.

177
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:06,120
I won't let you work for nothing.

178
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:08,260
I really don't know any magic.

179
00:10:09,750 --> 00:10:10,610
Are you scared?

180
00:10:11,270 --> 00:10:11,870
Nonsense.

181
00:10:12,360 --> 00:10:13,560
Why would I be scared?

182
00:10:14,200 --> 00:10:15,130
This entire town

183
00:10:16,320 --> 00:10:17,520
belongs to my family.

184
00:10:21,870 --> 00:10:23,240
That demon has a deep connection

185
00:10:23,240 --> 00:10:24,630
with your family.

186
00:10:25,040 --> 00:10:26,000
Maybe this demon

187
00:10:26,030 --> 00:10:27,080
was released by

188
00:10:27,100 --> 00:10:28,030
your ancestors.

189
00:10:29,510 --> 00:10:31,310
The one who started the trouble
must end it.

190
00:10:31,310 --> 00:10:32,910
Hurry up and find the magic book.

191
00:10:32,910 --> 00:10:33,510
Right now.

192
00:10:33,960 --> 00:10:35,560
Come to town with me tonight.

193
00:10:42,150 --> 00:10:42,750
Sorry,

194
00:10:42,960 --> 00:10:44,200
the number you dialed

195
00:10:44,240 --> 00:10:45,240
is out of service,

196
00:10:45,270 --> 00:10:47,270
and cannot be reached temporarily.

197
00:10:48,750 --> 00:10:49,840
You're getting bolder.

198
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:51,030
Not coming home at night
without telling me.

199
00:10:51,030 --> 00:10:51,960
Look!

200
00:10:52,480 --> 00:10:54,390
So handsome. Look!

201
00:10:54,390 --> 00:10:55,510
So handsome.

202
00:10:56,000 --> 00:10:57,330
What are you looking at?

203
00:10:58,180 --> 00:10:59,110
Director, look.

204
00:10:59,440 --> 00:11:00,560
That's Wang Fang's boyfriend.

205
00:11:00,560 --> 00:11:01,560
He's so handsome.

206
00:11:01,630 --> 00:11:03,120
Right? Right?

207
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:04,510
So handsome and tall.

208
00:11:05,000 --> 00:11:06,000
They are kissing.

209
00:11:10,910 --> 00:11:12,150
Yuanji?

210
00:11:13,320 --> 00:11:13,920
Director,

211
00:11:14,080 --> 00:11:15,480
do you play that game too?

212
00:11:15,670 --> 00:11:16,360
What game?

213
00:11:16,910 --> 00:11:18,310
The game Wang Fang plays.

214
00:11:18,600 --> 00:11:20,120
Once she reaches
a million intimacy points,

215
00:11:20,120 --> 00:11:21,670
the character she chose in the game

216
00:11:21,670 --> 00:11:22,930
will come into her life

217
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:23,960
and date her.

218
00:11:24,200 --> 00:11:25,080
He really came.

219
00:11:31,480 --> 00:11:31,910
Hello?

220
00:11:32,270 --> 00:11:33,670
Ya, you're up early.

221
00:11:34,120 --> 00:11:35,650
I have something to ask you.

222
00:11:36,790 --> 00:11:37,510
Yuanji

223
00:11:38,510 --> 00:11:40,110
is a character from the game.

224
00:11:40,460 --> 00:11:41,320
He relies on the adoration

225
00:11:41,320 --> 00:11:42,920
of those women to gain power.

226
00:11:43,240 --> 00:11:43,790
When this power

227
00:11:43,790 --> 00:11:45,080
is strong enough,

228
00:11:45,480 --> 00:11:47,250
he can appear in real life,

229
00:11:47,390 --> 00:11:48,120
just like me.

230
00:11:48,620 --> 00:11:49,600
You still remember

231
00:11:49,600 --> 00:11:51,080
that I used to be a painting, right?

232
00:11:51,080 --> 00:11:52,630
Doesn't that make him a demon?

233
00:11:52,630 --> 00:11:53,550
Is he absorbing

234
00:11:53,550 --> 00:11:55,010
Wang Fang's vital energy?

235
00:11:56,720 --> 00:11:57,790
What are you laughing at?

236
00:11:57,790 --> 00:11:58,360
I really thought

237
00:11:58,360 --> 00:12:00,020
you had turned over a new leaf.

238
00:12:00,320 --> 00:12:01,850
There's a huge difference.

239
00:12:02,080 --> 00:12:02,880
That girl

240
00:12:02,910 --> 00:12:03,480
knows

241
00:12:03,480 --> 00:12:04,880
what price she has to pay.

242
00:12:05,120 --> 00:12:05,870
She knows?

243
00:12:06,600 --> 00:12:08,630
Yeah, go ask her yourself.

244
00:12:13,800 --> 00:12:14,440
Wang Fang.

245
00:12:18,270 --> 00:12:19,200
You need to leave

246
00:12:19,230 --> 00:12:20,200
your boyfriend now.

247
00:12:20,200 --> 00:12:20,750
Why?

248
00:12:21,040 --> 00:12:22,000
He's not human.

249
00:12:22,200 --> 00:12:23,000
I know that.

250
00:12:24,020 --> 00:12:25,080
Aren't you scared?

251
00:12:25,150 --> 00:12:26,320
He treats me very well.

252
00:12:26,320 --> 00:12:27,520
Why would I be scared?

253
00:12:27,720 --> 00:12:29,480
Don't you think this relationship

254
00:12:29,480 --> 00:12:30,390
is super eerie?

255
00:12:30,910 --> 00:12:31,720
Director.

256
00:12:32,240 --> 00:12:33,390
Look at me.

257
00:12:33,630 --> 00:12:34,560
I'm so ordinary.

258
00:12:35,000 --> 00:12:36,270
I'm no stunning beauty,

259
00:12:36,270 --> 00:12:37,870
nor do I have a wealthy background.

260
00:12:37,870 --> 00:12:38,910
Normally,

261
00:12:39,240 --> 00:12:41,100
why would Yuanji ever fall for me?

262
00:12:41,390 --> 00:12:41,720
Look.

263
00:12:42,270 --> 00:12:43,650
The diamond ring he bought me.

264
00:12:43,650 --> 00:12:44,500
Do you know

265
00:12:44,530 --> 00:12:45,990
what price you have to pay?

266
00:12:47,440 --> 00:12:48,330
It doesn't matter

267
00:12:48,330 --> 00:12:49,730
as long as I can afford it.

268
00:12:52,960 --> 00:12:53,600
Director,

269
00:12:54,000 --> 00:12:55,460
why do you look so haggard?

270
00:12:55,630 --> 00:12:56,890
Did you not sleep well?

271
00:12:57,120 --> 00:12:58,840
Go back to your seat and rest a bit.

272
00:12:58,840 --> 00:13:00,440
I'll make you a cup of coffee.

273
00:13:29,480 --> 00:13:30,080
Director.

274
00:13:30,480 --> 00:13:31,480
Have some coffee.

275
00:13:31,510 --> 00:13:32,310
Okay, thanks.

276
00:13:44,790 --> 00:13:45,720
Get back to work.

277
00:13:54,550 --> 00:13:56,030
Dongqing's car lights are on.

278
00:13:56,030 --> 00:13:56,830
I'll go check.

279
00:14:08,550 --> 00:14:09,150
Dongqing!

280
00:14:10,510 --> 00:14:11,110
Dongqing!

281
00:14:12,150 --> 00:14:12,750
Dongqing!

282
00:14:14,200 --> 00:14:15,030
Open the door!

283
00:14:18,520 --> 00:14:19,250
Are you okay?

284
00:14:22,240 --> 00:14:22,970
Are you hurt?

285
00:14:28,960 --> 00:14:30,420
Do you remember anything?

286
00:14:31,720 --> 00:14:32,580
I only remember

287
00:14:33,550 --> 00:14:34,360
heavy rain

288
00:14:34,360 --> 00:14:35,160
pouring down.

289
00:14:36,750 --> 00:14:38,200
Then I couldn't see anything.

290
00:14:38,200 --> 00:14:40,400
I only heard the sound of flowing water.

291
00:14:41,790 --> 00:14:42,650
It sounded like

292
00:14:44,150 --> 00:14:45,560
a beast roaring.

293
00:14:46,270 --> 00:14:46,940
What beast?

294
00:14:48,030 --> 00:14:49,560
I've never heard it before.

295
00:14:49,670 --> 00:14:50,870
It sounded like a cow,

296
00:14:51,240 --> 00:14:52,790
but deeper

297
00:14:52,910 --> 00:14:53,970
and more shocking.

298
00:14:55,320 --> 00:14:56,320
A bit like thunder.

299
00:14:56,320 --> 00:14:57,240
This demon really doesn't

300
00:14:57,240 --> 00:14:58,040
mean any harm.

301
00:14:58,360 --> 00:14:59,410
It left you here

302
00:14:59,440 --> 00:15:00,170
in one piece.

303
00:15:02,440 --> 00:15:03,000
You guys

304
00:15:03,440 --> 00:15:04,240
saw the demon?

305
00:15:04,960 --> 00:15:06,420
He's a handsome young man.

306
00:15:06,630 --> 00:15:07,550
That's just an avatar.

307
00:15:07,550 --> 00:15:08,840
His name is Bai Xiaonian.

308
00:15:08,840 --> 00:15:09,770
It's a fake name.

309
00:15:09,870 --> 00:15:10,910
But it doesn't matter.

310
00:15:10,910 --> 00:15:11,710
Let's go back.

311
00:15:12,000 --> 00:15:12,550
Go back?

312
00:15:12,720 --> 00:15:13,620
What else?

313
00:15:14,320 --> 00:15:15,910
You've been missing all night.

314
00:15:15,910 --> 00:15:17,310
Isn't your wife worried?

315
00:15:17,720 --> 00:15:18,120
Right.

316
00:15:18,240 --> 00:15:18,600
I need to hurry up

317
00:15:18,600 --> 00:15:19,530
and call my wife.

318
00:15:19,910 --> 00:15:20,840
What do you mean?

319
00:15:21,000 --> 00:15:21,720
You quit?

320
00:15:22,720 --> 00:15:23,510
That demon

321
00:15:23,810 --> 00:15:25,030
just wants to protect this town

322
00:15:25,030 --> 00:15:25,840
from invasion.

323
00:15:25,840 --> 00:15:26,770
It means no harm.

324
00:15:26,790 --> 00:15:28,320
I don't think it's necessary
to eliminate it.

325
00:15:28,320 --> 00:15:30,380
Then what about my development plan?

326
00:15:30,440 --> 00:15:31,700
You accepted my money.

327
00:15:32,050 --> 00:15:34,240
Ms. Huang, your memory isn't very good.

328
00:15:34,240 --> 00:15:35,790
I already returned the money to you.

329
00:15:35,790 --> 00:15:36,270
Besides,

330
00:15:36,270 --> 00:15:38,070
why must you develop this place?

331
00:15:38,700 --> 00:15:40,500
It's such a beautiful small town

332
00:15:40,630 --> 00:15:42,560
with hundreds of years of history.

333
00:15:43,080 --> 00:15:44,830
You insist on tearing it down
to build villas.

334
00:15:44,830 --> 00:15:46,160
But will they even sell?

335
00:15:47,550 --> 00:15:48,270
I'm done reporting.

336
00:15:48,270 --> 00:15:49,690
My wife was worried sick.

337
00:15:49,870 --> 00:15:51,000
What's the plan now?

338
00:15:51,960 --> 00:15:52,980
Let's go home.

339
00:16:02,840 --> 00:16:03,570
Huang Shang!

340
00:16:11,510 --> 00:16:13,030
Huang Shang, where are you going?

341
00:16:13,030 --> 00:16:14,240
None of your business.

342
00:16:14,240 --> 00:16:15,370
I do whatever I want.

343
00:16:15,840 --> 00:16:17,120
I'm going to slay the demon.

344
00:16:17,120 --> 00:16:17,920
Are you crazy?

345
00:16:19,360 --> 00:16:20,560
Are we still leaving?

346
00:16:22,430 --> 00:16:24,270
Didn't you hear?
She does whatever she wants.

347
00:16:24,270 --> 00:16:25,580
What a stubborn woman.

